'''Marwa Zein ni''' umunya [[Sudani]] ukora ibintu byinshi harimo umuyobozi wa firime , umwanditsi wumwanditsi hamwe nuwatunganya film . Niwe mwanditsi wa documentaire ya 2019, ''Khartoum Offside'', akaba n'umwunganira uburenganzira bw'umugore binyuze mu mirimo ye. <ref>https://www.filmlinc.org/daily/new-york-african-film-festival-goes-virtual-with-streaming-rivers-the-past-into-the-present/</ref> <ref>https://actfilmfest.colostate.edu/films/khartoum-offside/</ref> Niwe washinze ORE Production, isosiyete ikora firime ya Khartoum ishingiye kuri Khartoum akaba n'umwe mu bakinnyi ba firime barindwi batoranijwe baturutse hirya no hino ku isi kugira ngo yitabe iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2019 n'ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga rya Emerging Film Talent Association (IEFTA). <ref name="Can">https://www.iefta.org/seven-filmmakers-to-attend-cannes-2019/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Ku mushinga we wo gutanga impamyabumenyi, Zein yanditse, ayobora kandi akora filime ngufi ya documentaire,  ''A Game'', mu 2009, ihindurwa mu ndimi eshanu kandi itangwa nk'umuntu watoranijwe ku mugaragaro mu minsi mikuru mpuzamahanga 30. mu Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Dubai 2016 (DIFF), film ye ngufi, a week'', two days'', yakinnye na Yasmin Raies na Amro Saleh, <ref>https://cinando.com/en/Film/one_week_two_days_341027/Detail</ref> yerekanwe bwa mbere. <ref>http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/5/32/245240/Arts--Culture/Film/-Egyptian-film-One-Week-Two-Days-to-compete-in-th-.aspx</ref> Yagaragaye no mu bindi birori bitandukanye bya firime. <ref>https://womenandhollywood.com/hot-docs-2019-women-directors-meet-marwa-zein-khartoum-offside/</ref>

Mu gutunganya iyi filime, yamaganye imyifatire mibi ya guverinoma ya Sudani ku ruhare rw’abagore mu gukina filime. <ref>https://www.broadwayworld.com/bwwtv/article/NEW-YORK-AFRICAN-AMERICAN-FILM-FESTIVAL-Goes-Virtual-Dec-2-20201119</ref> Nubwo atigeze ahura n’umubiri ku buryo butaziguye mu gihe cyo gukora iyi filime, yakiriye iterabwoba rya kamera cyangwa ibikoresho bishoboka ko byangirika. <ref name="Q">https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20200218-the-worlds-most-fearless-filmmakers</ref> <ref>https://debalie.nl/cinema/idfa-khartoum-offside-by-movies-that-matter/</ref> <ref>https://44.mostra.org/en/filmes/impedimento-em-cartum</ref> Amaherezo ariko, yabonye uruhushya rukenewe rwo gufata iyi firime. Nyuma y’impinduka za politiki zazanywe n’impinduramatwara ya [[Sudani]] yo muri 2018/19, iyi filime yerekanwe ubwo hafungurwaga iserukiramuco rya sinema ryigenga rya Sudani i Khartoum muri Mutarama 2020. <ref>https://sudanow-magazine.net/page.php?Id=903</ref>

